divs: Sighting DetailsWe lived on a air force base in 1991. My daughter then 10 and my son 4 went out to play in the back yard with friends. I was washing dishes, when I had an overwhelming feeling to go check on my kids. I went out and my daughter said that she saw a ufo. The other kids were excited as well. My daughter said to look up and all I saw was a golden streak go into the clouds. My daughter said that it looked like a diamond with a wheel going around it.
